          "Moment of Registration",
          "Initial Dataset comprised about 3000 students but was subsequently cut to 776 instances.\n\nLater, due to class imbalance (only 86 students had faild to complete degree) authors decide to create their models on a subset of 100 students (50/50).\n\nAuthors develop their own sets of features and test their effectiveness.",
