    {
      "id": "18f4750c-f3ba-807b-9c91-d8e856b5a16a",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "EDM and LA are useful disciplines to extract insights from educational databases. Most of themethods that predict student performance use income or assets, but often neglect spending or personal information. ",
